{"tid":1779799,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"神人一掌擊破「5層樓瓦片」！網友全看傻：傳說中的練武奇才？","createTime":"2019-12-12T02:06:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T03:37:07.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"69b573cf0ffe5325d86685d3078da588b2b2bbba","tid":1779799,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T02:06:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/joko.dwi.5688/videos/377363973014503/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjoko.dwi.5688%2Fvideos%2F377363973014503%2F&d=WPWOQTheSiAT%2FB2p9vAnAEt47LdDf8L2Tg6pYSR3Psk%3D&h=bab5d3b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/joko.dwi.5688/videos/377363973014503/</a><br />\n<br />\n擊破木片或瓦片是空手道或跆拳道常見的表演，不過通常最多5至6片。國外近日有一則劈瓦的影片在網路上瘋傳，只見一位神人一口氣徒手擊破「5層樓高」的瓦片，力量之強大讓網友全都讚嘆不已，直呼「根本是練舞奇才阿！」<br />\n <br />\n影片是由網友「Joko Dwi Priyono Priyono」分享至臉書，從影片中的場景來看，當天應該是在一個軍事集會現場，畫面中充斥著許多身穿迷彩制服、頭戴亮橘帽的阿兵哥，前方用鷹架架起的舞台上則有一位武術人員站在高處，將約莫1層樓高的瓦片徒手擊破，這時台下也傳來一陣歡呼以及掌聲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4570/d4570081.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4570%2Fd4570081.jpg&h=ce609192&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4570/d4570082.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4570%2Fd4570082.jpg&h=40ef9671&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n接著鏡頭一轉，又出現了3座更高的舞台，前方一樣放著同等高的瓦片，尤其是在中間那座，目測約有5層樓高，站在上面的武術人員先是集氣了約20秒，接著一口氣徒手將眼前的「瓦片高樓」給擊碎。<br />\n <br />\n這部94秒的影片一曝光後就引起熱烈討論，不少網友紛紛讚嘆表示，「好功夫！」、「太強啦」、「練到死也沒這麼猛」、「降龍十八掌」、「傳說中的練武奇才？」但也有許多網友狂批根本就是假的，「力量不可能傳導這麼遠」、「我怎看都是推倒的，跟武術無關」、「幼稚園小朋友也做得到」、「疊這麼高，當然一推就會倒阿」。"},{"pid":"1082eb7db42ba7f805281d73405cd22f7f70a9fd","tid":1779799,"uid":112416,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T02:12:36.000Z","msg":"啲瓦片打到碎曬喇，好痛心"},{"pid":"1ccc118a690cde218ec0bff87dcfc7bac5f0b1b0","tid":1779799,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T02:20:17.000Z","msg":"大佬 擺明跌爛架喎"},{"pid":"5b09c7b005b3d10205e0de42915a0b8f27e039fa","tid":1779799,"uid":73935,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T02:24:12.000Z","msg":"如果佢打落地下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n地球RIP"},{"pid":"0642168955b08e6726bdb26626436c7100dd7154","tid":1779799,"uid":128981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5b09c7b005b3d10205e0de42915a0b8f27e039fa","tid":1779799,"uid":73935,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T02:24:12.000Z","msg":"如果佢打落地下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n地球RIP"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T02:25:15.000Z","msg":"龍珠咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e02e44ddbf1d03d3827e890385b8ed73e7242a47","tid":1779799,"uid":71657,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T02:25:33.000Z","msg":"少林寺批貨原來運咗比佢"},{"pid":"d92835e70cefcebbb69a57dc2844552edb65e787","tid":1779799,"uid":48887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T02:27:16.000Z","msg":"On79<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"717d2c48be036ca428db4ab4800224ca1547d971","tid":1779799,"uid":187241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T02:28:16.000Z","msg":"擺明骨牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留意每一磈中間都有空隙 頭幾個爛左會向下跌，之後下邊個啲會因為上邊跌落黎嘅重量壓碎，如此類推。 如果全部排到密一密都打得碎就勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b9bebfa35724fcca98fdcf0f43395c9c3c3a2e2","tid":1779799,"uid":293588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T02:28:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae48fdc6810505d76aee7e6dbaf52fb5ce983a2","tid":1779799,"uid":254684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited